{"analytics_identifier":"EA63","base_path":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency","content_id":"240f72bd-9a4d-4f39-94d9-77235cadde8e","description":"The Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency regulates medicines, medical devices and blood components for transfusion in the UK. MHRA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Department of Health and Social Care .","details":{"acronym":"MHRA","alternative_format_contact_email":"webupdates@mhra.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency regulates medicines, medical devices and blood components for transfusion in the UK.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency\">MHRA</abbr> is an executive agency, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care\">Department of Health and Social Care</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-of-health","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Medicines &amp; Healthcare products<br/>Regulatory Agency"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"},{"href":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"},{"href":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency/about/procurement","title":"Procurement at MHRA"},{"href":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency/about/recruitment","title":"Working for MHRA"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/mhra-approves-beremagene-geperpavec-vyjuvek-for-the-treatment-of-dystrophic-epidermolysis-bullosa","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a076251229555d0fe8266d6/s712_pexels-skelm-7856727__2___1_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a076251fcae986635db904a/s465_pexels-skelm-7856727__2___1_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a076251279ebb7d24f8f364/pexels-skelm-7856727__2___1_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-15T19:09:20.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>As with any medicine, the MHRA will keep the safety and effectiveness of Vyjuvek under close review.</p>\n\n</div>","title":"MHRA approves beremagene geperpavec (Vyjuvek) for the treatment of dystrophic epidermolysis bullosa"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/mhra-supports-northern-ireland-life-sciences-sector-with-new-hub","image":{"alt_text":"MHRA CEO Lawrence Tallon with partners from DfE, DoH, HIRANI and Invest NI. ","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a04599f4fb0713aa63ea85d/s712_Resize_image_project__2_.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a04599f81a251700a20b4ff/s465_Resize_image_project__2_.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a04599fe71c4cdf4026bb00/Resize_image_project__2_.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-13T11:37:27.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The MHRA hub in Belfast will strengthen collaboration and engagement with local industry, academia and the healthcare sector.</p>\n</div>","title":"MHRA supports Northern Ireland life sciences sector with new hub"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/mhra-strengthens-safety-warnings-for-finasteride-and-dutasteride","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01df6be71c4cdf4026b9e3/s712_pills_3_960_640.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01df6be71c4cdf4026b9e2/s465_pills_3_960_640.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01df6b2a6137e93226b999/pills_3_960_640.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-11T14:43:56.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Updated safety advice has been issued to strengthen warnings about potential psychiatric and sexual dysfunction linked to finasteride and to provide precautionary advice on dutasteride.</p>\n</div>","title":"MHRA strengthens safety warnings for finasteride and dutasteride"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/mhra-opens-uk-wide-consultation-on-redefining-gene-therapies","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01d4148cc72d2f863ea72c/s712_DNA_strand__2___1_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01d414cd2e0e8b5b20b3e0/s465_DNA_strand__2___1_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01d41481a251700a20b3a3/DNA_strand__2___1_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-11T14:00:52.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>To future-proof the sector and ensure regulation keeps up with scientific and technological developments, the MHRA is consulting on proposed changes to how gene therapies are defined in UK legislation.</p>\n</div>","title":"MHRA opens UK-wide consultation on redefining gene therapies"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/mhra-invites-views-on-proposed-changes-to-medical-device-regulation","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01af21cd2e0e8b5b20b393/s712_Clinical-Immunology-Service-2.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01af21cd2e0e8b5b20b391/s465_Clinical-Immunology-Service-2.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a01af218cc72d2f863ea6e1/Clinical-Immunology-Service-2.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-11T11:26:00.0